error.message: Parameter $event of method Drupal\cache_control_override\EventSubscriber\CacheControlOverrideSubscriber::onRespond() has typehint with deprecated class Symfony\Component\HttpKernel\Event\FilterResponseEvent: since Symfony 4.3, use ResponseEvent instead
Value of core_version_requirement: ^8 || ^9 is not compatible with the next major version of Drupal core. See https://drupal.org/node/3070687.
Add core_version_requirement: ^8 || ^9 to designate that the extension is compatible with Drupal 9. See https://drupal.org/node/3070687.
